{"tid":2063111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗暴一年】自由廣場晚會逾7千人撐港 黃之鋒：盼今天台灣，明天香港","createTime":"2020-06-13T15:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T16:09:45.000Z","uid":226955,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0598a0722ad56e7e9411e76251bfc4d963eea956","tid":2063111,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:41:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200613/76XSMM5SKX3CKR3GD6L3DCAZRQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200613%2F76XSMM5SKX3CKR3GD6L3DCAZRQ%2F&d=8Hffn7AX%2B5q16JKWebZXJkPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=fcfaf7c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200613%2F76XSMM5SKX3CKR3GD6L3DCAZRQ%2F&h=506aced7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200613/76XSMM5SKX3CKR3GD6L3DCAZRQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n好似要會員先可以入到，所以我喺度節錄一part比大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n香港反送中運動1周年，台灣10多個公民團體今晚6時於台北市自由廣場，舉行「抗爭未完，台港同行」周年晚會，要求蔡英文政府盡速兌現庇護港人方案的承諾，除邀請香港知名作詞人林夕、銅鑼灣書店店長林榮基上台發言，另邀各政黨代表出席。官方公佈，至今已有超過7,000人出席。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒透過預錄的聲援影片表示，面對北京日益嚴重壓迫，港台是命運共同體，未來國安法的目標是台灣，盼台灣政府要避免黑警、親北京資本家入侵。黃也提及「今天香港，明天台灣」，希望未來是「今天台灣，明天香港」，希望香港人可以和台灣人一樣體現民主，擁有自己選政府的機會。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n主辦團體呼籲，中國對香港承諾的「港人治港」及「一國兩制」地位已崩解，沒有實現的承諾，不能算是承諾，盼相關政策須按蔡總統承諾，及早落實援助機制。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m0wz3V8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm0wz3V8.jpg&h=f11b8d86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n多謝台灣人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港台友好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b184046f3041832cbeade03166ace5a9da855f","tid":2063111,"uid":269481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:41:53.000Z","msg":"多謝台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf861c11e43b8a493d322c68fbad700c03b9d20","tid":2063111,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e65a7ad595ba2d3a83ad0166a7ad2b23c9ca03","tid":2063111,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:43:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75c47dd27d0b9ddeda190371904b57a9c51fad9c","tid":2063111,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:57:55.000Z","msg":"多謝"},{"pid":"32bb734a3a93e8796d6dc24f2a4415a21ef444d6","tid":2063111,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:04:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2cc1658b10e5d532ce1ce062d98d1365b877ab2b","tid":2063111,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T16:07:06.000Z","msg":"感謝臺灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d0a97f0d931bdf948607b8297e41d0ae842f40","tid":2063111,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0598a0722ad56e7e9411e76251bfc4d963eea956","tid":2063111,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T15:41:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200613/76XSMM5SKX3CKR3GD6L3DCAZRQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F